OL,3,CMan killed before he could reunite
OL,4,Cwith mum for first time in 24 years
OL,6,F"Imagine how excited his mother must
OL,7,Fhave been, to reunite with her baby
OL,8,Fafter many years, to explore how much
OL,9,Fhe has grown since they last saw each
OL,10,Fother," Alex's sister said.
OL,12,FMalcolm, from Eastville, was acquitted
OL,13,Fof murder but found guilty of
OL,14,Fmanslaughter and possession of a
OL,15,Fbladed article following a trial at
OL,16,FBristol Crown Court.
OL,18,FHe has now been sentenced to 13 years
OL,19,Fand six months in prison for the
OL,20,Fkilling.
