OL,3,CMan killed before he could reunite
OL,4,Cwith mum for first time in 24 years
OL,6,FThe court heard the pair had a long-
OL,7,Frunning personal dispute. On
OL,8,FValentine's Day of this year, they
OL,9,Fwere involved in an altercation in
OL,10,FGrosvenor Road, St Pauls, and Malcolm
OL,11,Fsustained a cut above his eye.
OL,13,FThree weeks later - on 5 March -
OL,14,FMalcolm was seen driving around St
OL,15,FPauls in a borrowed car for more than
OL,16,Fan hour until he found Alex. During a
OL,17,Fbrief confrontation, he fatally
OL,18,Fstabbed him in the upper thigh.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
