OL,4,Cwith mum for first time in 24 years
OL,6,FAlex was taken to hospital but,
OL,7,Fdespite the best efforts of medics,
OL,8,Fdied.
OL,10,FAlex's sister said his loved-ones
OL,11,Flives have been "on standstill" since
OL,12,Fhis death. She spoke of the "trauma,
OL,13,Fpain and heartache" that came with the
OL,14,F"realisation Alex is never coming
OL,15,Fback".
OL,17,FShe also spoke of Alex's plans of his
OL,18,Fambitions to open a restaurant and how
OL,19,Fjust the week before his death he'd
OL,20,Fasked her to go and help research
OL,21,Fpossible locations for the venture.
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@EO]
