OL,3,CMan killed before he could reunite
OL,4,Cwith mum for first time in 24 years
OL,6,FShe added: "Knowing that we will never
OL,7,Fhear his keys opening the door at
OL,8,Fhome, never hear his voice, his laugh,
OL,9,Fhis silly jokes, see him do silly
OL,10,Fdances, never hear him say 'ite, go
OL,11,Fon' (which was his way of saying bye)
OL,12,Fagain ` we will all need to learn to
OL,13,Flive without Alex because someone was
OL,14,Fso selfish as to kill our brother,
OL,15,Fson, uncle, nephew, grandson, friend,
OL,16,Fpartner, mentor, support system and
OL,17,Fanything else that he may have been to
OL,18,Fanyone in his life."
OL,26,@nD@LOUzD@TO]
