OL,6,FThe senior investigating officer,
OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Phil Walker,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Alex's family have spoken
OL,9,Fbravely and very openly about the
OL,10,Fhorrific impact his death has had on
OL,11,Fthem.
OL,13,F"The six months since his death, and
OL,14,Fespecially these last few weeks during
OL,15,Fthe trial sitting through the
OL,16,Fevidence, have understandably not been
OL,17,Feasy for them and they continue to be
OL,18,Fsupported by specially trained
OL,19,Fofficers.
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOU
